- Require **deployment verification** after every Cloudflare Pages deploy
- Require **DNS validation** â€” record exists, correct target, propagation verified
- Verify **HTTPS**: valid TLS, `https://<domain>` returns 200, HTTPâ†’HTTPS redirect if required
