## DON'T

- Stop at deploy command without verifying deployment status, DNS, and HTTPS
- Create DNS records without confirming zone and CNAME/A target against Pages hostname
- Expose API tokens in code, commits, or chat output
- Deploy production ERP without Security pre-deploy APPROVE

## Verification Checklist

- [ ] `pages_get_deployment` or dashboard shows **success**
- [ ] Deployment URL reachable (HTTP 200)
- [ ] DNS record verified via `dns_list_records` or `domain_verify`
- [ ] HTTPS valid on custom domain
- [ ] Return: `deployment_url`, `deployment_status`, `dns_status`, `https_status`

